name: PHOTO - HENOWEEN 1 "PAGODA"
description:
This is a photo of a mystical structure.
It houses the spirits of animals and people.
Some find themselves at it's door.
Are you lucky enough to enter?
Will you visit those who dwell inside?
Will you return?

HAPPY #HENOWEEN

photo by HP LoveBux
Franklin Park, Boston MA
October 2021
